---
title: Soy & Honey Salmon Parcel with Coconut Rice
description: Cooking fish in a parcel is a great way to keep it moist and flavourful. Chefs call this 'en papillote' which literally means 'in parchment'. You can, of course, use baking paper but it's easier to create a tight seal with foil so that's what we're going for today. Give it a try -  you've got dinner all wrapped up!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/soy-honey-parcel-ff5dd92f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/soy-honey-parcel-354a32f3.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/soy-honey-parcel-594bed622310a82a865cc202
